column1: 1 Please note these figures are estimates. Although they are rounded to the nearest ten people
column2: they cannot be guaranteed to be precise even to that level of detail.

column1: 2 The method used to produce the estimates updates the back years so figures for previous years are revised each time estimates are produced for the latest year. This is why the figures are labelled as provisional.
3 Figures may not add due to rounding.
4 The 90 & over totals are also rounded to the nearest 10 in the table for consistency. However
column2: please note that unrounded 90 & over totals are published in the Mid Year Estimates
